Package: wcvpdata
Type: Package
Title: World Checklist of Vascular Plants Data
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Paul E.",
                    family = "Santos Andrade",
                    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                    email = "paulefrens@gmail.com",
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6635-0375")))
Maintainer: Paul E. Santos Andrade <paulefrens@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a local interface to the 'World Checklist of Vascular
    Plants' (WCVP) <https://powo.science.kew.org/about-wcvp> (Version 15,
    January 2026), sourced from 'Plants of the World Online'
    <https://powo.science.kew.org/>. Bundles standardized snapshots of global
    taxonomic and geographic distribution data for vascular plants, designed
    to support large-scale botanical research and biodiversity analysis
    directly in 'R'.
